---
layout: layout.njk
pagination:
  data: collections.all
  size: 10
  reverse: true
  alias: posts
---
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="container flex">
      <div class="flex-column">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <p>Hey I'm Aman Thakur. I am a front end developer and love working with modern JS. I often blog about my coding adventures here.</p>
        <p>I initially started my career as a marketer and then switched to developer when exposed to programming. Because of my initial career, I am also very keen to develop apps that are conversion-friendly, fast and rank well in search engines.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-column">
        <img class="hero-image" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dksughwo7/image/upload/v1580483332/hacker-journey/aman.png" alt="aman" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="posts">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Blog Posts</h2>
      {% for post in posts %}
        <article>
          <h3>
            <a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h3>
          <span>posted on </span><time datetime="{{ post.date | dateIso }}">{{ post.date | dateReadable }}</time>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
